// Fragment file for daily-standup.kdl — the message template steps.
//
// A wflow include fragment is a bare list of step nodes (no schema/id/
// title/recipe wrapper). The including file's recipe block splices these
// in place at decode time.
//
// To customize the message: edit the `type` strings below. Variables
// like {{ticket}} and {{eta}} are resolved against the including file's
// vars + captured shell output, so the same fragment can be reused
// across multiple standup workflows with different bindings.

type "Yesterday: shipped {{ticket}}, reviewed two PRs."
key "shift+Return"
type "Today: ETA on the rollout is {{eta}}, then digging into the spike for next week."
key "shift+Return"
type "Blockers: none."
key "Return"
